{"tid":856023,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"成日都諗住公司樓下郵局counter妹","createTime":"2018-10-10T11:12:42.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-10T11:22:53.000Z","uid":58316,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"4e2906d107bf0cde05bc7d718d00d9693806f723","tid":856023,"uid":58316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T11:12:42.000Z","msg":"幫公司攞信<br />\n有時要攞郵包包裹<br />\n唉條女真係好正<br />\n真係唔敢正眼望佢<br />\n只敢趁佢耷底頭做野<br />\n偷偷𥄫幾眼<br />\n有時見其他麻甩佬<br />\n寄野寄盛<br />\n借d意撩佢<br />\n佢又受<br />\n仲flirt返條麻甩佬轉頭<br />\n可能呢d唔叫flirt<br />\n只係我敏感左<br />\n但足以唔開心成日<br />\n見佢戴住隻戒指<br />\n唔知佢老公咩樣<br />\n但如果我係佢老公<br />\n見佢咁同其他男人講野<br />\n一定嬲到喊"},{"pid":"c2d0b6c3fd2209e8d391517f7b76f3da88d4004e","tid":856023,"uid":130678,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T11:14:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/10/191433_353706b1dbd9201d0f5dd7a7e00e4276.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F10%2F191433_353706b1dbd9201d0f5dd7a7e00e4276.gif&h=eda6f1d6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d313bed3946868963afd0277c6bb0dbb8df0ad6f","tid":856023,"uid":186282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T11:22:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/10/192242_748a79bc1958ab3d4b7ae671c3c14805.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F10%2F192242_748a79bc1958ab3d4b7ae671c3c14805.gif&h=8aad7366&s={SIZE}\" />屌你老母"}]}